00:18:13.360 --> 00:18:15.329 position:24% line:83% align:start
So if you show off
your intelligence a bit,

00:18:15.362 --> 00:18:18.198 position:19% line:83% align:start
Nadia will fall for you
over and over again.

00:18:18.231 --> 00:18:20.868 position:27% line:83% align:start
She's still just
a regular girl like the rest.

00:18:20.902 --> 00:18:22.436 position:35% line:89% align:start
Oh, I see.

00:18:22.469 --> 00:18:25.405 position:10% line:83% align:start
You're saying I should study
and invent some more.

00:18:25.439 --> 00:18:28.241 position:13% line:83% align:start
But Sanson told me I should
develop my muscles

00:18:28.275 --> 00:18:29.343 position:27% line:89% align:start
to win her over.

00:18:29.376 --> 00:18:31.478 position:33% line:83% align:start
Well, that's
some interesting advice.

00:18:31.512 --> 00:18:33.681 position:24% line:83% align:start
But let me ask you
an important question, Jean.

00:18:33.715 --> 00:18:35.883 position:7% line:89% align:start
See any girls in love with him?

00:18:35.917 --> 00:18:37.619 position:7% line:89% align:start
[Jean] I better start studying.

00:18:37.652 --> 00:18:39.353 position:10% line:89% align:start
I will capture Nadia's heart

00:18:39.386 --> 00:18:42.289 position:10% line:83% align:start
by applying myself to achieve
higher knowledge.

00:18:42.322 --> 00:18:44.191 position:30% line:83% align:start
To start with,
I'll prove my theory

00:18:44.224 --> 00:18:46.193 position:19% line:83% align:start
that the sun is moving
slowly now

00:18:46.226 --> 00:18:48.195 position:33% line:83% align:start
because this
island is heading west.

00:18:48.228 --> 00:18:49.597 position:35% line:89% align:start
Hey, Jean!

00:18:49.631 --> 00:18:51.766 position:27% line:83% align:start
-Studying again?
-No, I'm not studying right now.

00:18:51.799 --> 00:18:53.735 position:10% line:83% align:start
I'm calculating this island's
location.

00:18:53.768 --> 00:18:55.235 position:16% line:89% align:start
Calculating and whatnot?

00:18:55.268 --> 00:18:56.904 position:30% line:83% align:start
That certainly
sounds like studying to me.

00:18:56.938 --> 00:18:58.539 position:19% line:89% align:start
Never mind all of that.

00:18:58.573 --> 00:19:00.775 position:19% line:83% align:start
If you stop exercising
and keep calculating,

00:19:00.808 --> 00:19:02.877 position:16% line:83% align:start
you'll turn into an ugly
purse bag like Hanson.

00:19:02.910 --> 00:19:04.946 position:7% line:89% align:start
But Hanson told me to do this.

00:19:04.979 --> 00:19:07.715 position:30% line:83% align:start
Otherwise, I'll
become a stupid muscle head.

00:19:07.749 --> 00:19:09.316 position:21% line:89% align:start
Is that what he said?

00:19:11.451 --> 00:19:12.486 position:41% line:89% align:start
Wrong!

00:19:13.655 --> 00:19:15.723 position:21% line:89% align:start
Don't listen to him.

00:19:15.757 --> 00:19:16.924 position:33% line:89% align:start
Listen here.

00:19:16.958 --> 00:19:18.726 position:10% line:89% align:start
When a woman looks for a man,

00:19:18.760 --> 00:19:20.327 position:16% line:89% align:start
she is trying to acquire

00:19:20.360 --> 00:19:22.897 position:7% line:83% align:start
that which she does not possess
herself.

00:19:22.930 --> 00:19:24.866 position:7% line:83% align:start
Now, do you know the one thing
men have

00:19:24.899 --> 00:19:26.601 position:30% line:83% align:start
that women are
looking for?

00:19:26.634 --> 00:19:27.467 position:35% line:89% align:start
A mustache?

00:19:27.502 --> 00:19:28.603 position:47% line:89% align:start
No!

00:19:28.636 --> 00:19:30.470 position:41% line:83% align:start
-Power.
-Ah!

00:19:30.505 --> 00:19:31.572 position:33% line:89% align:start
That's right.

00:19:31.606 --> 00:19:33.741 position:35% line:83% align:start
Men protect
their power with muscles.

00:19:33.775 --> 00:19:34.676 position:24% line:89% align:start
Well, the women...

00:19:34.709 --> 00:19:36.276 position:38% line:89% align:start
Yes, yes.

00:19:36.309 --> 00:19:37.344 position:35% line:89% align:start
They cook!

00:19:37.377 --> 00:19:38.813 position:44% line:89% align:start
Jean!

00:19:38.846 --> 00:19:40.748 position:33% line:83% align:start
Why do I get
the sneaking suspicion

00:19:40.782 --> 00:19:43.584 position:16% line:83% align:start
that we're drawing closer
to death with each forkful.

00:19:43.618 --> 00:19:44.952 position:27% line:89% align:start
This is madness.

00:19:44.986 --> 00:19:47.955 position:7% line:83% align:start
You cannot go on letting Nadia
cook our food like this.

00:19:47.989 --> 00:19:50.490 position:10% line:89% align:start
It's not something I decided.

00:19:50.525 --> 00:19:52.760 position:30% line:83% align:start
She asked me if
she could try it again.

00:19:52.794 --> 00:19:54.662 position:5% line:89% align:start
And I said that she could do it.

00:19:54.696 --> 00:19:58.432 position:13% line:83% align:start
Yes, but don't you remember
what happened last time?

00:19:58.465 --> 00:20:00.535 position:13% line:89% align:start
It's only the second time.

00:20:00.568 --> 00:20:03.236 position:5% line:83% align:start
If she doesn't get any practice,
she will never improve.

00:20:03.270 --> 00:20:05.673 position:27% line:83% align:start
But if she keeps
practicing like this,

00:20:05.707 --> 00:20:09.242 position:16% line:83% align:start
certain young men may go
to heaven before she improves.

00:20:09.276 --> 00:20:10.545 position:16% line:89% align:start
Well, it's not as though

00:20:10.578 --> 00:20:12.980 position:10% line:83% align:start
her cooking is any different
than Ms. Granva's.

00:20:13.014 --> 00:20:15.348 position:10% line:89% align:start
I'd like you to name one time

00:20:15.382 --> 00:20:17.852 position:21% line:83% align:start
my cooking has killed
anyone, Sanson.

00:20:17.885 --> 00:20:20.822 position:7% line:83% align:start
Oh, now, Nadia didn't intend to
do anything wrong,

00:20:20.855 --> 00:20:22.557 position:19% line:89% align:start
so we should be kinder.

00:20:23.390 --> 00:20:26.527 position:13% line:83% align:start
So if we die and she meant
no harm, that's fine with you?

00:20:26.561 --> 00:20:29.530 position:19% line:83% align:start
Now don't read too much
into what I said, Sanson.

00:20:29.564 --> 00:20:31.699 position:19% line:83% align:start
Look, spicy food tastes
much better

00:20:31.733 --> 00:20:33.534 position:24% line:83% align:start
than the bland fair
you enjoy.

00:20:33.568 --> 00:20:36.704 position:10% line:83% align:start
Ah! Would someone deliver me
from this terrible island

00:20:36.738 --> 00:20:39.006 position:33% line:83% align:start
so that I can
eat some real food?

00:20:39.040 --> 00:20:40.775 position:10% line:83% align:start
[Ayerton] Hanson, why haven't
you gotten the Gratan fixed yet?

00:20:40.808 --> 00:20:42.309 position:16% line:89% align:start
What are you waiting for?

00:20:42.342 --> 00:20:43.477 position:21% line:83% align:start
Because you're always
taking Jean

00:20:43.511 --> 00:20:44.846 position:7% line:89% align:start
away to work on your projects.

00:20:44.879 --> 00:20:45.880 position:21% line:89% align:start
[Jean] That's enough!

00:20:48.415 --> 00:20:49.650 position:16% line:89% align:start
Can't you see it's silly

00:20:49.684 --> 00:20:51.519 position:10% line:83% align:start
to fight about such trifling
matters?

00:20:51.552 --> 00:20:53.453 position:24% line:89% align:start
Leave Nadia alone.

00:20:53.487 --> 00:20:54.622 position:44% line:89% align:start
Jean.

00:20:54.655 --> 00:20:55.923 position:41% line:89% align:start
Right.

00:20:55.957 --> 00:20:58.059 position:27% line:83% align:start
You must maintain
the health of the group.

00:20:58.092 --> 00:21:00.762 position:24% line:83% align:start
That is a sure way
to ensure happiness for all.

00:21:00.795 --> 00:21:03.497 position:35% line:83% align:start
These petty
arguments tear the very fabric

00:21:03.531 --> 00:21:05.600 position:21% line:83% align:start
that keep this little
community together.

00:21:05.633 --> 00:21:09.070 position:21% line:83% align:start
Well, you speak like
a real-life count, Mr. Ayerton.

00:21:09.103 --> 00:21:11.773 position:33% line:83% align:start
Perhaps I had
you all wrong before now.

00:21:11.806 --> 00:21:16.443 position:19% line:83% align:start
Oh, yes. How I miss my
salad days in majestic England.

00:21:16.476 --> 00:21:19.013 position:10% line:83% align:start
My pockets were always filled
with gold

00:21:19.046 --> 00:21:21.448 position:19% line:83% align:start
and I never wanted for
anything.

00:21:22.617 --> 00:21:25.019 position:16% line:83% align:start
I invited so many ladies
to my birthday parties,

00:21:25.052 --> 00:21:28.055 position:10% line:89% align:start
which lasted for days on end.

00:21:28.089 --> 00:21:31.759 position:7% line:83% align:start
We served liqueurs and spirits
from every corner of the world

00:21:31.793 --> 00:21:34.929 position:10% line:83% align:start
and our tables groaned under
the most extravagant meals

00:21:34.962 --> 00:21:36.363 position:19% line:89% align:start
you could ever imagine.

00:21:36.396 --> 00:21:38.566 position:19% line:89% align:start
We feasted like kings.

00:21:38.599 --> 00:21:39.967 position:38% line:89% align:start
[exhales]

00:21:41.002 --> 00:21:42.036 position:41% line:89% align:start
Hello?

00:21:51.813 --> 00:21:53.446 position:27% line:89% align:start
He's a good boy.

00:21:53.480 --> 00:21:54.715 position:41% line:89% align:start
Who is?

00:21:54.749 --> 00:21:57.018 position:21% line:83% align:start
Not many men would be
as forgiving as he is.

00:21:57.051 --> 00:21:59.386 position:16% line:89% align:start
That is so rare anymore.

00:21:59.419 --> 00:22:00.955 position:24% line:89% align:start
Yes, ma'am. But...

00:22:00.988 --> 00:22:02.455 position:13% line:89% align:start
You don't have to tell me.

00:22:02.489 --> 00:22:04.692 position:30% line:83% align:start
You think he'll
lose interest in you?

00:22:06.426 --> 00:22:08.461 position:7% line:89% align:start
It can't be helped I'm afraid.

00:22:08.495 --> 00:22:10.631 position:38% line:83% align:start
Women are
always living with that fear.

00:22:10.665 --> 00:22:11.999 position:30% line:89% align:start
[Nadia] Really?

00:22:12.033 --> 00:22:15.603 position:24% line:83% align:start
[Grandis] Jealousy,
longing, attachment, anxiety.

00:22:15.636 --> 00:22:17.572 position:13% line:89% align:start
These complicated feelings

00:22:17.605 --> 00:22:20.107 position:13% line:83% align:start
are always raging around in
our heads.

00:22:20.141 --> 00:22:21.676 position:16% line:89% align:start
It reaches such a fervor

00:22:21.709 --> 00:22:24.111 position:10% line:83% align:start
that nothing else in our life
has meaning for us.

00:22:24.145 --> 00:22:27.114 position:38% line:83% align:start
We exert
everything for their sake.

00:22:27.148 --> 00:22:28.549 position:44% line:89% align:start
Huh?

00:22:28.583 --> 00:22:30.852 position:16% line:89% align:start
That's how love is, see?

00:22:32.186 --> 00:22:34.589 position:19% line:83% align:start
I've never been in love
with someone before.

00:22:34.622 --> 00:22:37.158 position:30% line:83% align:start
I never really
wanted to be in love ever.

00:22:37.191 --> 00:22:39.927 position:21% line:83% align:start
Still, I didn't think
it would hurt this much.

00:22:39.961 --> 00:22:42.830 position:10% line:83% align:start
Now that I know how it feels,
I think I was right.

00:22:42.864 --> 00:22:44.131 position:19% line:89% align:start
The pain is unbearable.

00:22:44.165 --> 00:22:46.534 position:27% line:89% align:start
You do love him.

00:22:46.567 --> 00:22:49.770 position:7% line:83% align:start
It seems like many of the nice
things in life

00:22:49.804 --> 00:22:51.806 position:27% line:83% align:start
have traps hidden
inside them.

00:22:51.839 --> 00:22:53.140 position:38% line:89% align:start
So true.

00:22:53.174 --> 00:22:55.408 position:24% line:83% align:start
I can't even count
how many times

00:22:55.442 --> 00:22:57.678 position:16% line:83% align:start
I've cried over being in
love before.

00:22:57.712 --> 00:22:59.080 position:41% line:89% align:start
Really?

00:22:59.113 --> 00:23:00.480 position:30% line:89% align:start
[Grandis] Yes.

00:23:00.514 --> 00:23:02.984 position:30% line:83% align:start
However, I can
remember each one clearly.

00:23:03.017 --> 00:23:05.987 position:13% line:89% align:start
All of those broken hearts.

00:23:06.020 --> 00:23:07.454 position:30% line:89% align:start
Tell me, Nadia.

00:23:07.487 --> 00:23:08.556 position:33% line:89% align:start
[Nadia] Yes?

00:23:08.589 --> 00:23:10.992 position:27% line:83% align:start
Was Captain Nemo
your father after all?

00:23:14.528 --> 00:23:17.397 position:35% line:83% align:start
I'm sorry,
that was impolite of me.

00:23:18.566 --> 00:23:21.569 position:5% line:89% align:start
It's all right. And yes, he was.

00:23:21.602 --> 00:23:24.672 position:33% line:83% align:start
We have both
suffered a loss then.

00:23:24.705 --> 00:23:27.440 position:16% line:83% align:start
Well, at least you still
have Hanson and Sanson.

00:23:27.474 --> 00:23:29.176 position:30% line:89% align:start
Yes, of course.

00:23:29.210 --> 00:23:31.979 position:5% line:89% align:start
But those two are like the moon.

00:23:32.013 --> 00:23:34.582 position:21% line:83% align:start
They circle around me
constantly,

00:23:34.615 --> 00:23:36.751 position:24% line:83% align:start
but they will never
get any closer.

00:23:40.855 --> 00:23:42.890 position:38% line:83% align:start
-Ah, yes!
-What is it?

00:23:42.924 --> 00:23:45.793 position:33% line:83% align:start
If you like,
you may call me Mama.

00:23:45.826 --> 00:23:47.561 position:33% line:89% align:start
[Nadia] Mama?

00:23:47.595 --> 00:23:51.799 position:13% line:83% align:start
[Grandis] If Nemo was here,
it may have come to pass.

00:23:51.832 --> 00:23:52.733 position:33% line:89% align:start
[Nadia] Mama.

00:23:55.970 --> 00:23:56.804 position:21% line:89% align:start
[singing in Japanese]

